This milestone made generation trustworthy. A **design-system list & picker**
landed alongside a real freeform LLM route and an image-URL pipeline, with
**LLM prop inference** filling in component props. A **persistent file-backed
store** means your work survives restarts, and a **hallucinated-component
linter** flags generated components that aren't actually in your library.
Under the hood, the runtime AI layer became **model/provider-agnostic**, with
a migration to Zod 4 and fixed turbo tooling and tests.

